<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_517_r2l10"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Görg / als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des handels <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_517_r2l11"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> getan ſüllen haben etc das haben wır <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_517_r2l12">haben wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> awſʒgeſandt von <expan>ſchedlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> leẅt <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_517_r2l13">dıe etlıchen den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> geſtoln vnd <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> haben vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_517_r2l14">dem lande ſchedlıchen ſeyn / <expan>Dıeſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> ſein noch nıht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_517_r2l15"><expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> herheim <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ wır niht eygentlıch <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wıe dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_517_r2l16">ſache gehandelt 
<add><ab facs="#facs_517_line_1592200842049_1584">vnd </ab></add> <expan>ergange<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeyn / wenn <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıeſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
