<ab>Görgen <expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan> Eglofstein</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Görg, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des handels
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> getan süllen haben etc., das haben wir
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu haben wir
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> awszgesandt von
                            <expan>schedlich<ex>er</ex></expan> lewt <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        die etlichen den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gestoln und
                            <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> haben und dem lande schedlichen seyn,
                                <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> sein noch niht <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        herheim <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz wir niht eygentlich
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, wie die sache gehandelt
                            <add>und</add>
<expan>ergange<ex>n</ex></expan> seyn; wenn <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> herheim <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> wir denn von
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> daran gemant, so wellen wir ewch darczu
                                <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
